&lt;p&gt;We are seeking a highly motivated and enthusiastic individual with anaesthetic experience to work within our Theatre team at the world renowned Stoke Mandeville Hospital. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We require:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;A Band 6 Operating Department Practitioner/ Anaesthetic Nurse to work in this internationally accredited teaching hospital. The role would involve working in various specialities including Trauma &amp; Orthopaedics, Gynaecology &amp; Obstetrics, Plastic Surgery and Spinal.&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;Applicants must be a Registered Nurse with an appropriate Anaesthetic course or a Registered ODP. &lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;We can offer:&lt;br /&gt;&lt;br /&gt;• Opportunities for career development and progression&lt;br /&gt;• Excellent staff benefits&lt;br /&gt;• Preceptorship programme&lt;br /&gt;• A varied and interesting working environment&lt;/p&gt;
